Class RangeObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • codingchallenge.RangeObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<RangeObject>

    public class RangeObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<RangeObject>
    comparable object holding zip code ranges and lengths with methods for detecting overlap with and merging with other instances of RangeObject.
